<span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِمَامٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a Register</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّبِينٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">clear.</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/36:12" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3717"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>12<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 36-13 selected" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱضْرِبْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And set forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّثَلاً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an example</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْحَـٰبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of the) companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْقَرْيَةِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the city,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَآءَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">came to it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمُرْسَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Messengers,</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/36:13" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3718"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>13<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></a></p>
<p class="ayah 36-14" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَرْسَلْنَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We sent</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْهِمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱثْنَيْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">two (Messengers)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَكَذَّبُوهُمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">but they denied both of them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَعَزَّزْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so We strengthened them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِثَالِثٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with a third,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقَالُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Indeed, We</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَيْكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّرْسَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) Messengers.`</span></span></span> <a href="#!/quran-wordbyword/36:14" class="ayahNumber" data-verse="3719"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </s