<p class="ayah 36-15" style="font-family: 'KFGQPC Uthman Taha Naskh';"><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) but</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَشَرٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">human beings</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّثْلُنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">like us,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنزَلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">has revealed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلرَّحْمَـٰنُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Most Gracious</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">any</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">thing.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top 